transcription: If you got together with a girl and her idea of sex was like that you put the tip of the head in and then after 10 seconds she's like oh that's enough, would you want to continue a sexual relationship with that girl? Okay maybe if she was really inexperienced or if you were really really into it and she was open to learning and open to experiencing more depth in her sex life then okay you might stick around but if that was it, that was what you got out of her and that's where it was going to stay, would you stick around with her? I wouldn't. And why would you blame a woman for doing the same?
